OL,3,CSeasonal workers on UK farms given
OL,4,C'unhealthy and dangerous' accommodation
OL,6,FThe windows on the accommodation at
OL,7,FLeabank Nursery are visibly in a state
OL,8,Fof disrepair, the furniture is
OL,9,Fstained, the heater doesn't work, and
OL,10,Feven the toilet is broken.
OL,12,FSeasonal workers from Central Asia
OL,13,Fcame to the UK on six month visas to
OL,14,Fsupport the country's agricultural
OL,15,Fsector, and their job was to grow and
OL,16,Fpick aubergines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
