OL,3,CSeasonal workers on UK farms given
OL,4,C'unhealthy and dangerous' accommodation
OL,6,FBut they were being charged #300 a
OL,7,Fmonth per person to live in the
OL,8,Fcaravans they said were "unhealthy and
OL,9,Fdangerous" - with three workers having
OL,10,Fto share two beds.
OL,12,F"The caravan was disgusting and cold,
OL,13,FAzamat Bekturov, a sesonal worker from
OL,14,FKazakhstan, told us.
OL,16,FHe showed us footage from his caravan
OL,17,Fat Leabank Nurswery, and told us how
OL,18,Fhe had to pay for it from the minimum
OL,19,Fwage job he was doing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
