OL,6,FThe owner of Leabank Nursery has
OL,7,Fdenied the allegations ITV News put to
OL,8,Fhim.
OL,10,FWe also shared our findings with the
OL,11,Flabour provider for this farm, who
OL,12,Ftold us the seasonal workers have
OL,13,Fsince been transferred elsewhere - and
OL,14,Fthey've reported the living and
OL,15,Fworking conditions to the Home Office.
OL,17,FThe farm in Essex is not the only
OL,18,Fplace we found concerns about
OL,19,Faccommodation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
