OL,6,FIn the northeast of Scotland,
OL,7,FCastleton in Aberdeenshire is one of
OL,8,Fthe country's biggest, most
OL,9,Fprestigious fruit farms.
OL,11,FFamily run, it is owned by Ross and
OL,12,FAnna Mitchell.
OL,14,FThey've had a visit from royalty in
OL,15,Frecent years, and their company
OL,16,Fwebsite boasts that you'll see their
OL,17,Ffruit on the shelves at major
OL,18,Fsupermarkets such as Marks and
OL,19,FSpencer, Tesco, Waitrose, and Lidl.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
