OL,4,C'unhealthy and dangerous' accommodation
OL,6,FHowever, workers have told us about
OL,7,F"overcrowding" in the static caravan
OL,8,Faccommodation provided to seasonal
OL,9,Fworkers.
OL,11,FITV News has obtained footage showing
OL,12,Ftwo people - sometimes strangers -
OL,13,Fsleeping almost side by side in small
OL,14,Fcaravan bedrooms.
OL,16,FThe workers tell us they do a physical
OL,17,Fjob by day, and then they "must sleep
OL,18,Fin one position because there is
OL,19,Fbarely room to move" for the six
OL,20,Fmonths they live on Castleton Farm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
