OL,6,FWe checked and this is well above the
OL,7,Fgoing rate for two-bed accommodation
OL,8,Fin the area.
OL,10,FFor context, a modern two-bedroom
OL,11,Fmodern apartment is commonly listed at
OL,12,Fless than half that price in the
OL,13,Fnearest towns.
OL,15,F"There's no privacy - you lose your
OL,16,Fdignity living like this," one worker
OL,17,Fat Castleton told us under the
OL,18,Fcondition of anonymity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
