OL,4,C'unhealthy and dangerous' accommodation
OL,6,FDespite paying such high rent already,
OL,7,Fthese workers told they have also been
OL,8,Fthreatened with a #100 fine if the
OL,9,Fcaravan is deemed to be untidy and
OL,10,Fthey say they face weekly inspections.
OL,12,F"We came here to do a job but this is
OL,13,Fnot how we expected workers in Great
OL,14,FBritain would be treated," the worker
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"It feels like we are being
OL,18,Fdiscriminated against."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
