OL,6,FWe can report that seasonal workers
OL,7,Fare not being given equal protections
OL,8,Fin law, and that is due to a legal
OL,9,Floophole identified in our
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FCaravan accommodation housing this
OL,13,Fmany people should normally require
OL,14,FHMO licences, and would normally be
OL,15,Fsubject to inspections by local
OL,16,Fauthorities - but caravans for
OL,17,Fseasonal farm workers are specifically
OL,18,Fexempt for this.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
