OL,6,FThe legislation is devolved, so we
OL,7,Fshowed our footage from Castleton to
OL,8,FScotland's First Minister who called
OL,9,Fit "deeply troubling".
OL,11,F"Those conditions look unacceptable,"
OL,12,FJohn Swinney said in response to the
OL,13,Fevidence we presented to him.
OL,15,F"Obviously the points you're putting
OL,16,Fto me about cost (of the caravan
OL,17,Faccommodation) are equally troubling
OL,18,Fas well."
