OL,6,F"We have supplied the UK's major
OL,7,Fsupermarkets for over 30 years. As
OL,8,Fpart of this we are independently
OL,9,Faudited regularly, which includes an
OL,10,Fassessment of how we treat our
OL,11,Fworkforce and our standard of
OL,12,Faccommodation; workers are randomly
OL,13,Fselected and interviewed as part of
OL,14,Fthis process.
OL,16,F"Our business is wholly reliant on
OL,17,Fhaving a team of workers to carry out
OL,18,Fall the husbandry, harvesting and
OL,19,Fpacking tasks involved with soft
OL,20,Ffruit. Without people to do this, we
OL,21,Fdo not have a business.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
