OL,6,F"There is not a workforce available
OL,7,Flocally to carry out these tasks, so
OL,8,Fwe must recruit from overseas and
OL,9,Ftherefore have to attract workers by
OL,10,Foffering good living and working
OL,11,Fconditions.
OL,13,F"It makes good business sense for us
OL,14,Fto have workers choose to return to us
OL,15,Fthe following year. Our returnee rate
OL,16,Fin 2024 from 2023 is 73% which I feel
OL,17,Fspeaks for itself."
