OL,6,FCastleton Farm adds that they are
OL,7,F"replacing static style caravans with
OL,8,Fmodern chalet style accommodation,"
OL,9,Fand say, "we take great pride in the
OL,10,Faccommodation and conditions we
OL,11,Fprovide," which they say "represents
OL,12,Fgood value compared with private
OL,13,Fsector accommodation."
OL,15,FITV News is not accusing either farm
OL,16,Fin our investigation of illegality.
