OL,6,FUltimately, government sets the rate
OL,7,Ffor how much seasonal workers can be
OL,8,Fcharged for accommodation, and it is
OL,9,Fgovernment that issues seasonal worker
OL,10,Fvisas to support Britain's
OL,11,Fagricultural sector - worth #14
OL,12,Fbillion to the UK economy.
OL,14,FBut neither government, nor local
OL,15,Fauthorities are checking the
OL,16,Fconditions are suitable, or that the
OL,17,Faccommodation fairly reflects what
OL,18,Fworkers are being charged.
